		<div class="outer">
			<h1>Arrangements of polytopes and the 1-Steiner problem</h1>

			<div class="inner">
				<p><a href="../Author/Boris-Aronov.html">Boris Aronov</a>,
<a href="../Author/Marshall-Wayne-Bern.html">Marshall Wayne Bern</a>,
and <a href="../Author/David-Eppstein.html">David Eppstein</a></p>

				<p>Cited by:</p>
				<ul>
					<li><a href="Complexity-of-projected-images-of-convex-subdivisions.html">Complexity of projected images of convex subdivisions</a></li>
					<li><a href="The-union-of-convex-polyhedra-in-three-dimensions.html">The union of convex polyhedra in three dimensions</a></li>
					<li><a href="The-common-exterior-of-convex-polygons-in-the-plane.html">The common exterior of convex polygons in the plane</a></li>
