					<li><a href="Sparse-arrangements-and-the-number-of-views-of-polyhedral-scenes.html">Sparse arrangements and the number of views of polyhedral scenes</a></li>
					<li><a href="A-simple-and-efficient-procedure-for-polyhedral-assembly-partitioning-under-infinitesimal-motions.html">A simple and efficient procedure for polyhedral assembly partitioning under infinitesimal motions</a></li>
